column1: Daily Weather Observations for Murrurundi Gap, New South Wales for June 2021
Prepared at 13:00 UTC on Monday 18 October 2021   IDCJDW2162.202106
Some cloud observations are from automated equipment; these are somewhat different to those made by a human observer and may not appear every day.
